Description:
    Connects the Infopark API with the Ruby on Rails application to provide inplace editing
    functionality. By default the html editor "redactor" is used.

Example:
    `rails generate cms:component:editing`
    `rails generate cms:component:editing --editor=redactor`

    Assets:
      app/assets/javascripts/editing_toggle.js.coffee
      app/assets/javascripts/editing.js.coffee

      app/assets/stylesheets/editing.css.less

    Misc: Executes editor dependent generator:
          `rails generate cms:component:editing:redactor`
